      "raw_text": "sment OF the Great Northern at st.\nPaul has Informed G. w. Mahoney,\ncity passenger agent, that the\nGreat Northern will work with the\nSpokane chamber Of commerce In\ndistributing advertising materia,\nabout the Inland Empire.\n\n\nAt one time Cashier Of q bank at\nBuffalo, John Seliger, a victim of\ndrink, is now a prisoner in the\ncounty Jail on a 80 day sentence\nfrom the police court. He was\ntwice arrested for intoxication in\nthe last 10 days.\n\n\nG. Robinson, Great Northern\nagent at Hillyard for three years,\nleft today for Bellingham, TO which\npoint he has been transferred."
